A Nigerian woman left many people in a state of shock after she publicly went on her knees begging her boyfriend of about 5 years who had just ended their relationship. Her shout in anger attracted the attention of other customers who watched the ugly scene. It is not yet known the exact part of Nigeria where the incident took place. However, it was obvious the boyfriend had had enough of her. People coud only watch as the drama unfolded. Many believe the guy must be very rich for her to be begging someone who obviously shamed and disgraced her in public. Watch video below: Lady causes a scene at an eatery after her boyfriend of 5 years ended their relationship. pic.twitter.com/zy7EsbhHsx Source